                     <interp inst="t18010218-81-victim516" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            .</p>
               <p>Second Count. Laying it to be the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18010218-81-victim520" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Hibbert
                  <interp inst="t18010218-81-victim520" type="surname" value="Hibbert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010218-81-victim520" type="given" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010218-81-victim520" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , 
               
                  <persName id="t18010218-81-victim522" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Hibbert
                  <interp inst="t18010218-81-victim522" type="surname" value="Hibbert"></interp>
